ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> 懷疑自己有</blockquote><br />\n上面有講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"454a3e2ec653a3457199c2f3aedd574389f95252","tid":180102,"uid":59546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4056624ef9447bf054bfade30285973a67054675","tid":180102,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實乜叫風濕 痛法係點？ 後生會唔會有？</blockquote><br />\n我咪後生有嘅活例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係骨入面痛出黎，唔同肌肉痛有得按下抒緩，好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n好似比人拎螺絲批鑽舊骨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又好似比蟲蛀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70ffb76d67a68b6340c7690a202da49a0450013","tid":180102,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:19:11.000Z","msg":"中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"062e31dad27763cdeaf9e20e545f108ebb99e2fb","tid":180102,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:23:53.000Z","msg":"個醫師話係啲血唔流通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"f8ebdf4c2aae6dd3575f9415188b8fed215dff1b","tid":180102,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T17:33:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實乜叫風濕 痛法係點？ 後生會唔會有？</blockquote><br />\n我咪後生有嘅活例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係骨入面痛出黎，唔同肌肉痛有得按下抒緩，好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n好似比人拎螺絲批鑽舊骨咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又好似比蟲蛀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 