00Z","msg":"<blockquote>中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日痛撚到想死<br />\n手腕腫痛已經當廢左成隻手<br />\n咩都做唔到咁濟"},{"pid":"af2769f056a98d99fa71dacdcf17d0c2e83a9384","tid":180102,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我係盆骨痛 一落雨前就痛到hihi<br />\n但我睇左好多次急症都話無野 我好feel到左邊盆骨係再突d 唔知中醫幫唔幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我諗中醫會好啲，西醫多數俾止痛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中醫會幫你調理好埋身體"},{"pid":"b92691fbb843c917bdedd24d6f1841193cd36d37","tid":180102,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日痛撚到想死<br />\n手腕腫痛已經當廢左成隻手<br />\n咩都做唔到咁濟</blockquote><br />\n我中四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日落大雨嘛 夏天成日落仲難受 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4190e58875ba6040df4b162f49960f04b27ce50","tid":180102,"uid":56018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日痛撚到想死<br />\n手腕腫痛已經當廢左成隻手<br />\n咩都做唔到咁濟</blockquote><br />\n我中四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日落大雨嘛 夏天成日落仲難受 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最開頭係自己踢波傷左膝頭<br />\n睇完跌打未好返晒就繼續踢波搞到膝頭有風濕<br />\n之後開始其他整親過既位置都開始會風濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後進化到而家冇整親既位都會痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手指痛果陣會揸唔到筆"},{"pid":"1b93a3d5e722de051a35553b80fd95850a857c15","tid":180102,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:30:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日痛撚到想死<br />\n手腕腫痛已經當廢左成隻手<br />\n咩都做唔到咁濟</blockquote><br />\n我中四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日落大雨嘛 夏天成日落仲難受 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痛完手跟著痛腳<br />\n睇撚左5年公立都唔可以舒緩痛症/斷尾<br />\n而家放棄治療算<br />\n睇唔睇都一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e0a812a9498958af898b15df183fc06356fbb43","tid":180102,"uid":89478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:36:52.000Z","msg":"風濕因為氣壓問題 落雨打風氣墮唔同左 個膝頭就好似有好多重野壓住咁 向內逼入去舊骨到 其實係大氣壓 無得醫 通常傷過 軟紅織有問題先會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713395c2b2eef435dc351e20bdbb82a89e0a7076","tid":180102,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:43:39.000Z","msg":"唔肯定係咪風濕<br />\n都係返風落雨會冤冤痛<br />\n小學時又係會痛到訓唔到<br />\n懷疑係細個做運動定行路姿勢唔岩<br />\n沖熱水涼之後會舒服少少"},{"pid":"6785e1d5d5748897ef11ca7aa5ed2f3583a97257","tid":180102,"uid":3052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T18:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>風濕因為氣壓問題 落雨打風氣墮唔同左 個膝頭就好似有好多重野壓住咁 向內逼入去舊骨到 其實係大氣壓 無得醫 通常傷過 軟紅織有問題先會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前睇私家個報告話我白血球數量過多<br />\n免疫系統失靈<br />\n之後先將我轉介到公立風濕<br />\n個醫生話天氣好似唔多關事<br />\n多數關個人體質事多"},{"pid":"3328ddf257dcb85be2dc38d746aa19207f7e5a11","tid":180102,"uid":89478,"like":