<br />\n我係冇啦啦有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多數膝頭，有時手肘<br />\n可能我整傷左我唔知掛</blockquote><br />\n女人更易有 唔夠鐵同鈣"},{"pid":"483e5bf9d4ce17faa6262e7dadc323b4062f6dfb","tid":180102,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:27:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>風濕因為氣壓問題 落雨打風氣墮唔同左 個膝頭就好似有好多重野壓住咁 向內逼入去舊骨到 其實係大氣壓 無得醫 通常傷過 軟紅織有問題先會痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁啲人話咩太寒又係咩一回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寒底 唔應該太補同食寒野</blockquote><br />\n我本身就係極寒底又中意食雪糕嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4301a01c4d881a96cd7b1f033bf2f8723d3a4d5f","tid":180102,"uid":93344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:28:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中三開始風濕<br />\n準過天文台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢幾日痛撚到想死<br />\n手腕腫痛已經當廢左成隻手<br />\n咩都做唔到咁濟</blockquote><br />\n我中四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日落大雨嘛 夏天成日落仲難受 撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最開頭係自己踢波傷左膝頭<br />\n睇完跌打未好返晒就繼續踢波搞到膝頭有風濕<br />\n之後開始其他整親過既位置都開始會風濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後進化到而家冇整親既位都會痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n手指痛果陣會揸唔到筆</blockquote><br />\n我係冇啦啦有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多數膝頭，有時手肘<br />\n可能我整傷左我唔知掛</blockquote><br />\n女人更易有 唔夠鐵同鈣</blockquote><br />\n咁我係咪飲紅棗水就解決到問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b7fbfaf4fcd9abec29ea52ea1d392728dc78d","tid":180102,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:46:2